entries.femaleVariant: [Sit] Where's Fingers?
[Sit] Fingers helps working folk?
Fingers a friend to the workin' guys and girls 'round here?
Fingers – where'll I find him?
Well, well, whadda we got here?
Nah, nah. I'd rather live here.
Is Fingers around?
Fingers – know where I can find him?
If I could I'd swap, y'know.
He's operatin' on somebody right now.
Helped me.
What're you doing here?
Glad you came.
Glad to see a familiar face.
I'm worried sick about her, V. Had no idea anything'd happened.
Fine... let her through, Sludge.
Helloooooo? There's a line...?
Been in there for ages… Shouldn't be much longer.
He chipped you some chrome with RealSkinn that had peeled off. What he replaced it with looks like a bathroom floor from a senior home.
Don't hold your breath. I've spent hours waitin' for him to come out.
[Sit] Seen a girl with blue hair here?
You seen a woman with blue hair around here? Had a doll chip.
Think Evelyn's being kept here somewhere?
Think I know who you're talkin' about... Fingers worked on 'er, sure.
Ey, not one step closer.
Don't start.
I don't want any trouble.
Looking for Fingers.
Look, I don't want any trouble.
Looking for a ripperdoc – goes by Fingers.
Just let me through, pretty please.
Who's askin'? And why?
Got a busted implant.
Not your biz.
My biz not yours. Lookin' for him 'cause I feel like it. Now get outta my way.
Got a problem with an implant.
Fuck off.
Yo, you hear what this bitch said to me? Best watch your tongue!
entries.maleVariant: Yo, you hear what this motherfucker said to me? Best watch your tongue!

entries.femaleVariant: Ain't you just the cutest thing.
If you're lookin' for a release, I just might be your man…
entries.maleVariant: If you're lookin' for a release, I just might be your match…

entries.femaleVariant: Best apologize for that, bitch!
Here to see who?
Got an issue needs sortin' out. Here to do that.
So how about you fuck off, let me through and no one will be the wiser?
How 'bout you pretty please me, hehe?
All riiiiight, all right, go on.
Know where I can find him?
I'd say it again. But what for? Your little skull sponge can't possibly get its grey cells around it.
Not from around here. Couldn't find another ripper in the city to patch you up?
Heard Fingers was the best.
Yeah, the best for joygirls. Are you a whore?
Yes.
No, but you are.
Kindly get the fuck outta my way.
An escort. For special tastes.
No, but you are – from the look of things.
Lookin' for a ripper who can cater to my special needs.
Good... Fingers'll like you. Let her through!
entries.maleVariant: Good... Fingers'll like you. Let him through!

entries.femaleVariant: Just don't turn off the lights.
Summer means rain, means I have to sit in the basement the whole time.
Why does everythin' have to be so damn... convoluted.
In the end, all you got left are shredded cables and empty bottles.
Nuh-uh, you ain't cuttin'!
Sit your ass down and wait your turn!
How'd you know where to find her?
You knew she wasn't at Clouds?
Mean to say, this whole time you knew Evelyn wasn't at Clouds?
Who do you take me for? Why would I lie about something like that?
Because you don't trust me?
What're you even doing here, Judy?
Same thing as you. Looking for Evelyn.
How'd you know to look for Evelyn here?
Got friends at Clouds. Word spreads out of there quicker than the clap.
Meaning?
Friend told me what you dug up, so here I am.
You're right, I don't. But that doesn't make me a liar.
You talk to Fingers yet?
You talk to Fingers yet?
This friend of yours – who is it?
If only. He's harder to get in to see than the best docs in town.
Tom Caldera. Works as a doll there.
Never bothered to mention Evelyn had disappeared when we talked. Then you came around asking questions. Got him scratching his head.
Didn't strike me as the brightest bulb of the batch.
Sorry, but right now I could give a shit about what does or does not strike you.
Let's just concentrate on finding Evelyn? I'm starting to get worried, seriously.
We'll find her, I know we will.
Specially when he collects "payment" right after the procedure! Hehehe.
She still here?
No idea. Gotta ask him.
I'd be in a wheelchair if it wasn’t for him.
Better than bein' a cripple.
On the one hand hope she is, 'cause I want her back fast.
But on the other, hope to God no, because who knows what that sick fuck could've done to her.
She means a lot to you, doesn't she?
And you've arrived at that conclusion how, exactly?
Moment you knew where she was, you sprang into action.
Once you get close to Evelyn, you never wanna let her go.
Fuck off and leave me be!
Think I'm scared of your skinny ass?
Tsk-tsk-tsk, so serious from the get-go? I was only joking, sheesh.
V, hey.
Made it all the way here, huh? Must really wanna talk to Evelyn…
You worked at Clouds?
Not as a doll. Tuned their virtus.
That's where I met Ev, Tom and the rest of the crew.
Hey, look in the mirror. Who paid for all that? Think Fingers woulda fixed a cracked faceplate for free? You want out, you gotta pay me back.
You will be when every Mox in town descends on this shithole.
You got a financial claim, take it to court, you pussy.
Fine, I get it. Everyone's got their breakin' point. Just pay me what you owe me and you can fuck off to greener pastures.
Hah! I don't owe you shit.
Oh, but you do. And that shit has a name – something around twenty thou.
What?! Come on, you pulled that number out of your ass!
Ey, watch that tone with me, ya skank.
All right, might've overdone it a smidge. Sorry.
Gotta be worth a damn to get an apology from me.
Nobody talks that way to Lil' Loco!
Nobody talks that way to us!
Too fucking late now! Can't unsay words you've said!
Fine. I overdid it.
I never apologize. To trash.
And you're trash, not worth shit.
Lil Loco'll just stuff 'em back down your throat till you choke!
You all right?
Hey, you all right?
No way I'm 'onna swim. I hate water.
Can't you see nobody cares?!
You know Fingers?
Fingers guy – you know 'im?
Heard some things, yeah…
Like...?
His hand sometimes slips.
Why'd Evelyn go back to Clouds?
After the heist, Evelyn holed up with the Mox for a while, right?
That's right.
So why the hell'd she go back to Clouds?
Thought she'd be safer there. God knows why.
Tried to get her to see straight, but she just wouldn't listen.
Hey, hands off her!
Fine, fine. I'll wait.
Everybody gotta wait their turn, that's the rule.
C'mon, let's go.
Need to talk to Fingers. It's important.
My friend here's in really bad shape. Could we cut in front?
Don't have time for this bullshit.
My friend here? She's in really sorry shape. Couldn't let us cut in front, just this once?
Aaaaarghh...
Sorry, don't have time to sit around.
Uh, that makes three of us.
[Stand]
I need to talk to him. It's important.
You think we're just here to polish our nails, hm?
I'll let you cut in front of me.
You're a real pain in my clit, Mitzy, know that? And you... might as well knock and find out when he's moppin' up.
S'posed to be a goddamn clinic, not an enny-op launderette.
'Course, honey, be my guest.
Well now, hold on, hold on a sec. Didn't seem so bad just a minute ago.
She's a toughie. Keeps it inside, mostly.
Go on, now, don't you worry about her.
Tell you what makes three. Number of seconds it'll take me to turn this place upside down, inside out.
Jeeeez, all right! You got nerve. Don't let me stop you if you're in such a goddamn hurry…
We're gonna be here forever, I just know it. Maybe you could talk to those girls, see if we can't cut in front?
Why me?
I don't think they like me. Just give it a shot. That or come up with something better.
The Mox got Fingers in their crosshairs?
Mox don't happen to have Fingers in their crosshairs?
Got a message from the Tyger Claws.
Got a message for Fingers. Comes from the Tyger Claws.
And that message would be...?
Two things – urgent and confidential.
Meaning?
Meaning you've got a choice.
You either get your shit kicked in for being slow or for being a nosy prick.
Oh yeah?
No. Why?
Heard joytoys come out of his clinic in worse shape than they come in.
Yeah, well... can't solve all the world's problems at once.
Woooo! Thass' right! You get 'em, girl!
entries.maleVariant: Woooo! Thass' right! You get 'em, boy!

entries.femaleVariant: Hope that teaches those candy-ass scopsuckers not to come 'round here no more.
Here. This oughta cover you for some real chrome. From a real ripper.
If you're flush enough to afford a "real ripper," then what're you doing here?
[Pay] Find yourselves a better ripperdoc.
Hell do you care? She's here 'cause she feel like it. Now thank the lady and le'ss you an' me delta.
entries.maleVariant: Hell do you care? He here 'cuz he feel like it. Now thank the man and le'ss you an' me delta.

entries.femaleVariant: Think Evelyn's here?
Evelyn – she means a lot to you.
You used to work at Clouds?
Who's this friend of yours?
[Wait] Fine, I'll wait.
[Sit] Fine, I'll wait.
Tha'ss just a straight circus act. Fuckin' a-cro-ba-tics, flyin' in an' shit?
Jus' watch you don't break your legs, honey? Gonna be beggin' Fingers for a new pair.
Yeh, yeh, twitty bird… heheh.
What's this? Lost your thunder?
Nuh-uh. Not gettin' anywhere that way.
Lost your way?
This way, that way… this a fuckin' a dance floor?
Eh. Nothing special.
